<li><span data-contrast="auto"> Personal data will be processed in order to set up an account in the Application created</span><br /><span data-contrast="auto">in the NAWA project entitled "</span><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">Pozostań&nbsp;w&nbsp;kontakcie&nbsp;z&nbsp;absolwentami&nbsp;PP</span><span data-contrast="auto">, Stay connected with PUT Alumni" aimed at integrating the environment of graduates of the Poznan University of Technology.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;469777462&quot;:[1200],&quot;469777927&quot;:[0],&quot;469777928&quot;:[1]}">&nbsp;</span></li>
